images.prompt: A haunting, high-detail digital portrait of a blood sorceress rendered in a cutout collage style, her form illuminated by floating prism light that casts shimmering hues across her algae green and cold iron attire, as glitching reflections ripple across her mystical figure, viewed from a light-through-hand perspective that emphasizes the ethereal, layered textures and surreal depth of her presence, blending fragmented paper-like elements with visceral blood-red accents and intricate, shadowed details that evoke an otherworldly aura of arcane power and spectral magic amidst a dreamlike, atmospheric canvas.

Amidst a tumultuous storm-lit sky, a regal cosmic whale queen with luminous bronze scales and gentle blush highlights gracefully emerges from shimmering water, her majestic form echoing vintage poster elegance, enhanced by a soft lens flare that dances across reflective, mirror-like waters, creating an immersive tableau of mythic grandeur and celestial serenity captured in exquisite detail through a richly textured digital artwork that melds realistic portrait finesse with an otherworldly, almost cinematic atmosphere.
